;
- (ii) The certificate holder must comply with the requirements of GACAR § 121.1409 for timelimited system planning.;
- (iii) The certificate holder must operate under the ETOPS authority as contained in itsoperations specifications.;
- (iv) The certificate holder must comply with the maintenance program requirements of GACAR § 121.671.;
